Reviews.Title: delivered on time but 3 connectors did not function
Reviews.Author: Todd Bittner
Reviews.Content: I ordered these connectors to hook up zmodo cameras where I had already run cat5e cable and did not want to have to run the cables that came with the cameras.  The BNC connectors and the female power connectors worked well but I had problems with 3 of 5 of the male power connectors that would not make positive connections and caused me to cut off the ends of the cables that came with the cameras and splice them to the cat5e cable to make the male power connections work.

Reviews.Title: Simple Install
Reviews.Author: KM
Reviews.Content: What more could one ask for?  Item arrived quickly and in good shape looks a little cheap but does the job to say the least would order again for the price.
